---
/* Maintenance landing — used by index.astro and dashboard.astro during
   Session 66 "Operation Clean Slate". The bot is paused; the public
   numbers were biased and are being rebuilt against Binance testnet.

   When the rebuild is done, both pages revert to their normal content
   (home: hero + bots + library, dashboard: live snapshot). Track the
   work in PROJECT_STATE.md. */
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 pt-16 pb-24 sm:px-6 sm:pt-24 sm:pb-32">

  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full
               border border-amber-400/30 bg-amber-400/5
               px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em]
               text-amber-400">
    <span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400
                 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(251,191,36,0.7)]"></span>
    Operation Clean Slate · Session 66
  </span>

  <h1 class="mt-7 text-[32px] font-semibold leading-[1.12] tracking-tight
             text-text sm:text-[40px] md:text-[44px] md:leading-[1.08]">
    The numbers are
    <span class="text-primary">under audit</span>.
  </h1>

  <p class="mt-6 text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-text-dim sm:text-[15.5px]">
    We're rebuilding the bot's accounting from scratch. The old
    paper-trading data carried a quiet bias we couldn't fix in place —
    so we stopped the bot, took a snapshot, and started over.
  </p>

  <p class="mt-3 text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-text-dim sm:text-[15.5px]">
    Trading is paused. The public numbers will be back when they're
    certified against Binance testnet — target
    <strong class="text-text">around May 17, 2026</strong>.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-5">
    <p class="font-mono text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em]
              text-text-muted">
      Meanwhile
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-[14.5px] leading-[1.55] text-text-dim">
      The diary keeps going. The story behind this audit is the next
      chapter of Volume 3.
    </p>
    <a href="/diary"
       class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[14px]
              text-primary hover:underline">
      Read how we got here
      <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-14 font-mono text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em]
            text-text-muted">
    — Session 66 · "Sometimes the bravest thing a CEO can do is admit
    the engine needs rebuilding, not another oil change."
  </p>
</section>
